       S3000-KJL0008-PROCESS-RTN.

           PERFORM  S3100-READ-FILE-RTN
              THRU  S3100-READ-FILE-EXT

           PERFORM  UNTIL  IN-EOF-Y

                    INITIALIZE    TKJL0008-KEY
                                  TRJL0008-REC

      *             그룹회사코드
                    MOVE  IN-GROUP-CO-CD
                      TO  KJL0008-PK-GROUP-CO-CD

170224*            고객식별자
                    MOVE  IN-BASE-YMD
                      TO  KJL0008-PK-BASE-YMD

      *             차주번호
                    MOVE  IN-CUST-IDNFR
                      TO  KJL0008-PK-CUST-IDNFR

                    #DYDBIO  SELECT-CMD-Y TKJL0008-PK TRJL0008-REC

                    EVALUATE  TRUE
                        WHEN  COND-DBIO-OK
                              PERFORM  S3200-KJL0008-UPDATE-RTN
                                 THRU  S3200-KJL0008-UPDATE-EXT
                        WHEN  COND-DBIO-MRNF
                              PERFORM  S3300-KJL0008-INSERT-RTN
                                 THRU  S3300-KJL0008-INSERT-EXT
                        WHEN  OTHER
                              MOVE 'KJL0008'
                                TO  XZUGEROR-I-TBL-ID
                              MOVE 'SELECT'
                                TO  XZUGEROR-I-FUNC-CD
                              MOVE  DBIO-SQLCODE
                                TO  XZUGEROR-I-SQL-CD
                              MOVE 'SELECT시 오류가 발생했습니다'
                                TO  XZUGEROR-I-MSG
                              #ERROR  CO-EBM03001
                                      CO-UBM03001
                                      DBIO-STAT
                              #OKEXIT CO-CHA-08
                    END-EVALUATE

                    PERFORM  S3100-READ-FILE-RTN
                       THRU  S3100-READ-FILE-EXT
           END-PERFORM
           .
       S3000-KJL0008-PROCESS-EXT.
           EXIT.
